<section class="persona-slide layout-2b-grid" id="persona-1-core"><div class="identity-panel"><div class="avatar-wrap"><img class="persona-avatar" src="assets/画像头像素材/保障型运维工程师.png" alt="保障型运维工程师"></div><div class="identity-name"><div class="name-line">保障型运维工程师</div></div><div class="identity-desc">一线运维偏监控保障，希望华为云监控与堡垒机一站式打通，减少手工与外部工具。</div><div class="identity-meta"><div class="meta-row"><div class="meta-label">部门</div><div class="meta-value">运维团队</div></div><div class="meta-row"><div class="meta-label">岗位</div><div class="meta-value">运维工程师</div></div><div class="meta-row"><div class="meta-label">知识<br>结构</div><div class="meta-value">领域：熟悉企业项目划分、接口级监控与发布活动保障<br>工具：CES、堡垒机、LTS、Grafana（补充）、ITSM 审批</div></div><div class="meta-row"><div class="meta-label">背景</div><div class="meta-value">职责覆盖运维全链路，实际偏重监控保障、堡垒机权限与告警配置；日常对接项目组与领导查看资源使用情况。</div></div></div><div class="one-sentence-need"><div class="osn-text">买了你的服务，就应该在你上面一站式打通。</div><div class="osn-source">— 运维工程师</div></div></div><div class="modules-panel"><div class="grid-module grid-module-resp-rings grid-anchor-start" style="grid-column: 1 / span 6;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="2" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="1" fill="white"/><rect x="9" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="1" fill="white"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="5" height="5" rx="1" fill="white"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="5" height="5" rx="1" fill="white"/></svg></span>工作职责</div><div class="module-body"><div class="resp-rings"><div class="ring-item" data-evidence="&quot;电商项目七八百个接口，要挨个去点&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><svg class="ring-svg" viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle class="ring-track" cx="32" cy="32" r="24"/><circle class="ring-fill" cx="32" cy="32" r="24" stroke-dasharray="150.8" stroke-dashoffset="82.9"/><text class="ring-pct" x="32" y="38" text-anchor="middle">45%</text></svg><div class="ring-label">监控看板与告警规则配置</div></div><div class="ring-item" data-evidence="&quot;我买了机器，我在这里应该是直接能看到的，现在却要手工去录&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><svg class="ring-svg" viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle class="ring-track" cx="32" cy="32" r="24"/><circle class="ring-fill" cx="32" cy="32" r="24" stroke-dasharray="150.8" stroke-dashoffset="98.0"/><text class="ring-pct" x="32" y="38" text-anchor="middle">35%</text></svg><div class="ring-label">堡垒机与主机权限开通</div></div><div class="ring-item" data-evidence="&quot;我的期望是我不需要用 Grafana 了&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><svg class="ring-svg" viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle class="ring-track" cx="32" cy="32" r="24"/><circle class="ring-fill" cx="32" cy="32" r="24" stroke-dasharray="150.8" stroke-dashoffset="120.6"/><text class="ring-pct" x="32" y="38" text-anchor="middle">20%</text></svg><div class="ring-label">发布活动接口级保障</div></div></div></div></div><div class="grid-module grid-module-collab-flow grid-anchor-end" style="grid-column: 7 / span 6;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="3" cy="8" r="1.5" fill="white"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="1.5" fill="white"/><circle cx="13" cy="8" r="1.5" fill="white"/><line x1="4.5" y1="8" x2="6.5" y2="8" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="9.5" y1="8" x2="11.5" y2="8" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2"/></svg></span>上下游协同</div><div class="module-body"><div class="collab-flow"><div class="flow-cell" data-field-key="demand_source"><div class="flow-cell-label">需求来源</div><div class="flow-cell-value">项目组、领导关注企业项目资源</div></div><div class="flow-cell highlight" data-field-key="deliverables"><div class="flow-cell-label">交付物</div><div class="flow-cell-value">监控看板、告警策略、堡垒机权限</div></div><div class="flow-cell" data-field-key="downstream_flow"><div class="flow-cell-label">下一步流转</div><div class="flow-cell-value">研发/业务使用堡垒与监控，运维评估变更</div></div></div><div class="kpi-block" data-field-key="kpi"><span class="kpi-label">站点可用</span>领导关注接口成功率等直观指标</div></div></div><div class="grid-module grid-module-scenario-grid grid-anchor-full" style="grid-column: 1 / span 12;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="2" y="3" width="12" height="9" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="5" y1="14" x2="11" y2="14" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="8" y2="14" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg></span>典型业务场景</div><div class="module-body"><div class="scenarios-grid-3"><div class="scenario-card" data-evidence="&quot;支持变量的话一套图只做一次&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><div class="scenario-image scenario-image-empty"><div class="scenario-placeholder-icons"><span class="tool-icon-tag">CES</span><span class="tool-icon-tag">监控看板</span></div></div><div class="scenario-caption"><strong>CES 监控看板按企</strong><br>CES / 监控看板</div><div class="scenario-desc">CES 监控看板按企业项目筛选资源</div></div><div class="scenario-card" data-evidence="&quot;我买了机器，我在这里应该是直接能看到的，现在却要手工去录&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><div class="scenario-image scenario-image-empty"><div class="scenario-placeholder-icons"><span class="tool-icon-tag">堡垒机</span><span class="tool-icon-tag">ECS</span></div></div><div class="scenario-caption"><strong>堡垒机为新购 ECS</strong><br>堡垒机 / ECS</div><div class="scenario-desc">堡垒机为新购 ECS 开通访问</div></div><div class="scenario-card" data-evidence="&quot;领导只看接口成功率等直观指标&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><div class="scenario-image scenario-image-empty"><div class="scenario-placeholder-icons"><span class="tool-icon-tag">Grafana</span><span class="tool-icon-tag">CES</span></div></div><div class="scenario-caption"><strong>大促发布时接口成功率</strong><br>Grafana / CES</div><div class="scenario-desc">大促发布时接口成功率盯盘</div></div></div></div></div><div class="grid-module grid-module-painpoint-list grid-anchor-start" style="grid-column: 1 / span 6;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2.5" fill="white"/></svg></span>核心痛点</div><div class="module-body"><ul class="painpoints-list"><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;买了新的机器如果没人通知，就不在监控范围内&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">堡垒机不同步</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">新购 ECS 需手工录入堡垒机，无接口同步，买机器场景频繁时成本高</span></li><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;报错50次时告诉我是哪个项目组异常&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">监控选配繁琐</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">看板需逐个选资源，期望按企业项目或正则批量筛选，七八百接口难选</span></li><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;数据库磁盘满了告警失效，有两个小时不知道&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">告警规则僵化</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">规则难覆盖多资源组合，生产测试混在一起，常需 Grafana 补位</span></li><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;面向研发跟业务，到我运维评估影响，审批同意后再执行&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">权限分享失控</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">数据库临时授权分享后不可控，期望审批流后再执行（详见 hover 访谈原话）</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="grid-module grid-module-titled-list grid-anchor-end" style="grid-column: 7 / span 6;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="2" y="3" width="2" height="2" fill="white"/><rect x="6" y="3" width="8" height="2" fill="white"/><rect x="2" y="7" width="2" height="2" fill="white"/><rect x="6" y="7" width="8" height="2" fill="white"/><rect x="2" y="11" width="2" height="2" fill="white"/><rect x="6" y="11" width="8" height="2" fill="white"/></svg></span>体验目标</div><div class="module-body"><ul class="generic-list"><li class="generic-list-item"><span class="gl-title">一站式</span><span class="gl-detail">买了华为云服务就在平台内打通监控、堡垒、日志，不必再推广多套系统</span></li><li class="generic-list-item"><span class="gl-title">可迁移</span><span class="gl-detail">新项目上线时有能力迁移/初始化监控与堡垒配置，而非全靠手工</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section>
