nce="&quot;报错50次时告诉我是哪个项目组异常&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="gl-title">告警智能</span><span class="gl-detail">报错 N 次时直接告知哪个企业项目异常，而非先选分组</span></li><li class="generic-list-item" data-evidence="&quot;支持变量的话一套图只做一次&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="gl-title">图表变量</span><span class="gl-detail">LTS/CES 支持变量过滤，一套图覆盖新增接口</span></li><li class="generic-list-item" data-evidence="&quot;3000个接口完全不知道是哪个被动了&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="gl-title">审计粒度</span><span class="gl-detail">CTS 需到 APIG 具体接口级，非仅实例</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="grid-module grid-module-painpoint-list grid-anchor-full" style="grid-column: 1 / span 12;"><div class="module-title"><span class="module-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2.5" fill="white"/></svg></span>核心痛点</div><div class="module-body"><ul class="painpoints-list"><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;数据库磁盘满了告警失效，有两个小时不知道&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">资源分组失效</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">曾选全部资源致 DB 磁盘满告警失效约 2 小时，后改企业项目仍只能单选</span></li><li class="painpoint-item has-inline-metric" data-evidence="&quot;买了新的机器如果没人通知，就不在监控范围内&quot;&#10;— 运维工程师"><span class="pp-title">新资源漏监控</span><span class="mention-badge">1/1</span><span class="pp-sep"> | </span><span class="pp-detail">他人新购机器/新 APIG 未通知则不在监控范围，故障不可见</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section>
